I roll the tank from the "room"[r]
and let the water from the pipe fill it up.[l][r]
[r]I wonder how long this tank will last.[r]
Well, it's good enough for now.[l] We'll use the piped water until it stops, then switch to the tank. When that runs out, we’ll go find more.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

