Alright, now for some food.[r]
We have about 30 hanging potatoes left, right?[l][r]
There were more here than in the lower levels, but we're starting to run low... But we'll be okay![l][r]
[r]...Honestly, I never thought the ropes those potatoes were hanging from would be edible. Same with the leaves.[l][r]
I expected them to be poisonous and make us really sick, but when they turned out to be safe, I danced! Literally danced![l] I danced and laughed till I cried.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

